<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.6.3">
<l>uḷaintiṭ ṭeḻunta matukai ṭavarka ḷulappil valiyā ravarpāl vayiram</l>
<l>viḷaintiṭ ṭateṉṟeṇ ṇiviṇṇōr parava vavarnā ḷoḻitta perumāṉ muṉanāḷ</l>
<l>vaḷaintiṭ ṭavillā ḷivalvā ḷeyiṟṟu malaipō lavuṇa ṉuṭalvaḷ ḷukirāl</l>
<l>aḷaintiṭ ṭavaṉkāṇ miṉiṉṟāyc ciyarā laḷaiveṇ ṇeyuṇṭāp puṇṭirun tavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great lord who, when the gods beseeched [him], being truly distressed,</l>
<l rend="indent">thinking of the ripening of enmity in Madhu and Kaitabha,</l>
<l>Ended the days of [those] indestructible strong [demons],</l>
<l rend="indent">the one long ago with a bent bow,</l>
<l>The one who, with sharp claws, mangled</l>
<l rend="indent">the strong dagger-toothed demon’s mountain-like body,</l>
<l>See, he is the one who was bound, having eaten the butter</l>
<l rend="indent">churned by the herder women today.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
